    note right of Iterating
        currentSegment() is valid when !isDone().
        next() advances iterator; transitions to Done when last segment is consumed.
    end note

    note right of Done
        Terminal state: isDone() returns true.
        currentSegment() throws NoSuchElementException in this state.
    end note
